          "description": "Sarah, my physician assistant, is absolutely outstanding\u2014by far my favorite provider. She is professional, highly knowledgeable, attentive, and, most importantly, very kind and non-judgmental. It is rare to encounter a clinician who combines such intelligence with genuine compassion for patients.\n\nSarah truly deserves recognition for the work she does. Providers like her are hard to find.\n\nI would also like to commend the front desk staff and the nurses\u2014they are consistently welcoming and helpful. Clearly, great care has been taken in hiring an excellent team. Outstanding work all around.",
