          "description": "Brought our young daughter in just before closing last night, nervous about a sudden high fever she'd come down with during our vacation. We were seen immediately and provided with the kindest of care. Everyone we interacted with was so polite, knowledgeable, and honest. We are so thankful for their service and for the peace of mind we left with. If we are ever in need of urgent care services again while in town, we will absolutely come here! Highly recommend.",
