          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAdNJp1DAOjM6N2KAP-VQUftOJ-8vkr-Zv8LdRrqI8JcXojdaz4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I called 10 minutes before they closed on a Saturday evening and they said come on in with my sick teenager.  They took my daughter immediately and did the necessary tests, all of the staff were patient and kind even though we were there at closing time.  They said not to worry they were there to help.  Our pharmacy was closed so they sent the prescription to CVS.  I went to CVS and their pharmacy too was closed.  I came back in the urgent care, and the doctor and nurses helped sort a solution to get her the necessary medication overnight until our pharmacy opened this morning.  I could not recommend them enough and grateful for their attention and care.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KcVh6SjVhREJOV1U0MlVrb3lTbGxpTkhFMExYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x9ee9dbda0e353e68!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnJqXzJ5aDBNWU42UkoySlliNHE0LXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
