          "description": "The people working there are very nice. That's about the only nice thing about the place.\n\nWhen I went, there were no doctors, only a physician's assistant. The X-ray technician had to travel from another location, so we had to wait. Then they had the biggest trouble sending me a copy of the X-rays. There is no online medical record system either. Basically only go there if you have the flu. Anything bigger than that you won't get the right medical attention.",
