          "description": "Given what a busy afternoon it was, I was treated quickly and in a warm and friendly manner. Maureen at the desk was welcoming, Zuliska, the medical assistant was lovely, and the physicians assistant who examined at my ears was very caring and knowledgeable; he even brought up a picture online to show me what was going on with my ear. I would definitely go back to MedRite.",
